Source: libi18n-langinfo-wide-perl
Section: perl
Priority: optional
Build-Depends: cdbs, debhelper (>= 5)
Maintainer: Kevin Ryde <user42_kevin@yahoo.com.au>
Standards-Version: 3.9.5
Homepage: http://user42.tuxfamily.org/i18n-langinfo-wide/index.html
Bugs: mailto:user42_kevin@yahoo.com.au

Package: libi18n-langinfo-wide-perl
Architecture: all
Depends: perl (>= 5.8.1), ${perl:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Langinfo functions with wide-char strings
 This is a variation of the I18N::Langinfo module returning Perl
 wide-char strings, rather than locale charset bytes like the plain
 langinfo() function does.
